title: The Mix of Draven

embed.description: Domics and Jomm took Draven's voice and remixed it. Don't be jealous. Domics: http://www.youtube.com/user/d0mics Jomm: http://www.youtube.com/user/flashj0mm Music by NΣΣT: https://soundcloud.com/neet **Created in collaboration with Riot Games**

body:
Acá les dejo el nuevo mix, en esta ocasión es de Draven, a mi me gusto.
Los otros mix son de [**Lux**](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VTaOzFVZIIY) , [**Braum**](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zYd8D804bT0) y [**Teemo**](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KDIAGsCOWD8) .
Saludos!
